name: Voxel Dreams: K-Food Series #06: Amazonian Palm Curry (bogsung-a yaja kale) 복숭아 야자 카레, by The Chef (a.k.a @wasem_simon)
description: Curry is a category of Asian dishes, in which each country brings its signature. Korean Kale, is soft on fragrance, but with a push on the bittersweet balance, bringing the strength of comfort food from the far east. The chef only brought the best of its traditional flavors, in modifying its notes, he adds the Amazonian heart of palm.
